Text: Dude, while I appreciate the effort to upload all of this...every file has at least one corrupted image, and they all have way too many .rar files that lead to nothing. WTF?

These are scene releases. ZIP files containing RAR files. Unzip all of the ZIP files and then use something like WinRAR to unpack the .RAR file to get at the images within. Nothing wrong with this release.

Thanks for a nice set of cuties, R0thschild.
